thread.title: ICBC Turkey Bank FY 2017 Net Profit Increases To 42.5 Mln Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: ICBC Turkey Bank FY 2017 Net Profit Increases To 42.5 Mln Lira
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - ICBC TURKEY BANK:
* REPORTED ON WEDNESDAY FY 2017 NET PROFIT AT 42.5 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 13.7 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET INTEREST INCOME AT 352.3 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 212.6 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NON-PERFORMING LOANS AT END-DECEMBER 96.4 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 115.0 MILLION LIRA AT END-DECEMBER 2016
Source text for Eikon:
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
